Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.02,0:00:05.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Black Organization member who infiltrated the hospital where Mizunashi Rena is being hospitalized...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:07.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kusada Rikumichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:11.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Killed himself after the FBI agent Akai and I cornered him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.07,0:00:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agent Akai claimed that if Kusada was able to make contact, the Organization would single out this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The FBI needed to perfect their plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:24.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of patients that can't be moved from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:34.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can we just wait here, knowing the Organization is coming, without alerting them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:36.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We won't just "wait."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:37.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll draw back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:39.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Draw back?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:41.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean leave her here and run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:44.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll draw back our bows and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not ambush them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:52.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The black wolves who've come to retrieve their straying colleague?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:01:02.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We discovered that Agent Akai snuck into the Black Organization in the past, and became the boyfriend of Haibara's older sister, Miyano Akemi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:09.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I'm able to escape from the Organization like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you go out with me as my real boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:22.47,Signs,,0,0,0,,Dai{\rHonorifics - Signs}-kun{\r}...\NIf I'm able to escape from the Organization like this, as my real boyfriend?\NAkemi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:28.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can we talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.69,0:01:33.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's about how we plan to attack them, I'm still thinking it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:35.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:37.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I saw you, I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just maybe you were thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:42.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly what I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:52.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, the one searching for his older sister, Hondou Eisuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Located Mizunashi Rena's hospital room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:01:59.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:01.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mizunashi Rena.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:06.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't ask you where my sister Hidemi is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:13.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're going take you somewhere again, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before that happens, open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:22.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:28.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:28.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:34.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:36.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you one of the new agents?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:41.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Andre Camel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:43.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I have a call from my wife right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:45.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:46.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a strategy session.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:54.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:14.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You never fail to amaze, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad you're an ally, Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:20.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:31.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now, Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In this match...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:41.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's live-or-die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you willing to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tingling suspense is building.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Running in the darkness —\ha red scream and a black shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:16.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victory hinges on some strange incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:17.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Each of them are related to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:23.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:44.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Conan is brought to you by these sponsors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:57.00,Title,,0,0,0,,CLASH OF RED AND BLACK\NDISTURBANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've prepared stretchers for the patients...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And three vans to transport them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:10.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the worst arises, we'll confuse them and flee with Mizunashi Rena in tow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:15.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I do hope we don't have to resort to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:16.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are there any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:18.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About communicating...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No cell phones or wireless devices, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, with this being a hospital, they can affect the medical equipment...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, cell phone calls are easy to tap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:35.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should anything happen, report it to your block leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:42.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your leader will then go outside and contact James via radio, who will be waiting in the parking lot to give instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:46.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't this too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:50.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we play the phone game with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:53.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They could end up taking vital tofu from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:57.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we are already prepared for an escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:07:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it's best we go for it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:04.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is our absolute last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since they still don't know which room is Mizunashi Rena's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moving her now is too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:16.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They definitely have their eyes on every car that comes and goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:22.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that we know their member Kusada was hiding an infrared thermographic device that detects heat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:30.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's likely that they'll discover which is our car from the number of people inside, thus making the FBI targets for their snipers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:35.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should that happen, we'll be escaping from bullets as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:39.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what if we need to contact you in an emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:44.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, contact me on my wireless if needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll leave that call to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:47.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:53.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, they likely won't come here wielding machine guns and handguns openly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They don't want the world to know of their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:07:58.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Creeping as if a shadow, vanishing like the fog...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's their trademark tactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:10.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The strategy session is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:15.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:22.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already know the plan from seeing the three stretchers here and the vans in the parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:25.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't say it's a "good" plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:27.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was expected, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:35.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,J-Just what is with you two!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:41.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it time for you to go home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:43.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:45.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told them I'd be staying at the Professor's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:47.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already took a quick nap, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:49.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:50.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:53.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let us know when you decide to flee, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:04.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm confident in my driving technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:07.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you seen that man before?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He only joined us recently, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, but I don't recognize his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:23.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would never forget an enemy face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's natural for him to appear recognizable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is a fellow FBI agent, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:34.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I still have a bad feeling about him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:47.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:50.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You aren't getting much sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:51.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are bags under your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those are normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:58.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'll go out for some fresh air while you patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought, Shuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's thinking too much about his murdered girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:10.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, with him, all we need is him thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:15.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he has been with them and understands their mindset...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:20.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's an opponent whose life they've already made multiple attempts on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the FBI's definitive trump card.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:42.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My stomach...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:45.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:49.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:53.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Toto line train is now arriving at Platform No. 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait behind the white line patiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:01.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-My throat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:02.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That strange smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:05.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Station attendant, please call for an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I can't get that notebook back...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's hearts will break!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fire has broken out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:18.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please follow the instructions of the nearby attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,James Black{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:36.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid we don't have a patient by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's not for a patient —\hit's for an attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:42.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person is a friend of mine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:44.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:45.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm here to deliver it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who sent you and what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:49.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:51.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sender was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One Kusada Rikumichi it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,K-Kusada Rikumichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep, you can guess what Kusada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} sent just from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Columbine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's known as "Odamaki" in Japan, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:16.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They sent this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:23.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since they used the name of their member who killed himself last night, there's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:28.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a precaution, we acted as security guards and checked all luggage of those entering the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:30.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We even checked delivery packages.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why would they send this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:36.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Columbine is a flower that grows in Colorado...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:37.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Obtain without failure."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the language of that flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:44.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it also means "clear victory."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a declaration of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:48.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:50.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're at the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:00.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are they fire victims from earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:02.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Meier at the entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So many ill patients and others are flooding the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't check them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:16.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those coming in are claiming there were three accidents that occurred simultaneously in the area!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:38.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three accidents at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:39.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:42.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Food poisoning, a disturbing odor, and a fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:44.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it their doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:49.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But while it's easy to control the timing of a disturbing odor and a fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:51.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Food poisoning symptoms show up at varying times from person to person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:56.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps they used a drug that emulates the appearance of food poisoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:14:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just the same, the other two accidents were set up in order to avoid killing anyone but also ensure they came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:10.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, after excluding those with surface injuries such as burns or cuts...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's still difficult to determine who is faking pain in their stomach, throat, and eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:24.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They can pretend to be victims of the accidents so as to get a large number of members into the hospital and quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:29.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their goal is, indeed, to locate the room where Mizunashi Rena is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:35.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they search in waves, they could find her very quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:43.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they're sending members in large numbers like that and having them act so suspiciously...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:48.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then they are giving us FBI agents a chance to apprehend some of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:52.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are not the types to take such risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, this uproar...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:57.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their target may be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:12.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear something just then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:14.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the flower pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:17.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's getting louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:23.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, there is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Put it on the ground and step away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bomb...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:09.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't even check the inside of the pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:13.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We thought they were only flowers, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:17.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Planting a bomb in a flower pot like this could only take out a few agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:24.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the explosion drew the Japanese police, searching for Mizunashi Rena would be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:27.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They could gain nothing from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:28.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what you thought, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:32.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, we have to get rid of the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:37.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's rigged with numerous traps, so defusing it will take too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The best and safest option is to take it to an unoccupied area and let it explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:44.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the timer is correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:48.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have 31 minutes and 14 seconds before it goes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, forgive me, but it's up to you, Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:54.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Shuu, you stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:56.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:59.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a garbage dump seven kilos from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:00.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go by car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:02.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then take my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:07.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you really have the time to make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:13.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The main roads are backed up due to the traffic caused by the three incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Making it in thirty minutes is questionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:20.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that is, unless you had a navigator like me with knowledge of the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:22.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, it's a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:23.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing away from your post?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:31.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard of the traffic problem with so many flooding the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:34.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came to report, since my post is nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured it was easier to approach you all directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:39.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no time to argue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:41.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You two get that bomb out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:42.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:45.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:47.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean Camel{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:51.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean, he doesn't have the friendliest face, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:56.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were gracious enough to include a visible timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:18:01.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, it was made to get louder so we would notice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, isn't it strange that they gave us more than thirty minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:13.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as if they gave the FBI enough time to take the bomb elsewhere to explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:16.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, what was the bomb meant for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:18.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what are they trying to do here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:33.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does this really lead to a shortcut to the dump?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:34.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was completely empty two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:40.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:43.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, did you put a clock in the trunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:47.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been hearing this ticking sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:50.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should have mentioned that earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:56.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There isn't a clock back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you really hear that back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and get in before I leave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:11.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you in the driver's seat now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:16.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be too tiring to direct you to the secret path aloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, I'm better than you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:22.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, there isn't a lot of time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you lie about the clock sound in the trunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:28.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sometimes lying is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:34.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on to it tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:53.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, the dump is the other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:55.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I gave up on that idea due to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:59.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All we need is an unoccupied place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:09.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and look at my kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:10.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot, I was here first!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:13.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, those delivery men...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:15.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there are a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:17.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:21.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:25.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:27.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kusada Rikumichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:32.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:33.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is everything going well on your end?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:35.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bomb should be going off soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:36.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:40.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agent Camel took the wheel...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:48.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Why open the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:48.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:51.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:54.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:09.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that noise!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:10.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:14.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, we've disposed of the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:16.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great job, Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:17.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:22.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If anything deserves praise, it's Agent Camel's driving technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:23.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:27.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And how are things on your end?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} seem to have found a clue as to what they're after.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:37.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm from security.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:41.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A nurse just brought you a package, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:43.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it from someone named Kusada?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:50.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I don't know anyone by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.07,0:21:51.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, allow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:01.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought: another bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:06.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a listening device.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They use it for a rising remittance fraud method.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.30,0:22:12.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-Bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:16.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So there really are bombs in those gifts?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.52,0:22:22.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of these plastic explosives will only blow one room.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:25.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if all of them go off at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.07,0:22:30.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The entire hospital will come down without a doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.41,0:24:03.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Four hours remain until the bombs delivered to the hospital go off.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:08.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We, after becoming aware of their aim, have come up with a risky plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.21,0:24:14.84,Signs,,0,0,0,,CLASH OF RED AND BLACK\NDISGUISE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.21,0:24:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time, on Detective Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.93,0:24:22.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Conan was brought to you by these sponsors.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.69,0:24:31.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.69,0:24:34.74,Signs,,0,0,0,,Driving Technique
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.78,0:24:34.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Driving Technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.07,0:24:36.62,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,March 3rd is "mimi no hi."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.62,0:24:37.37,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's also called Hinamatsuri, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.37,0:24:38.49,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Because it's a day for chicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.45,0:24:39.37,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
